@model DavidBrowning.Admin.ViewModels.Work.Experience.EditViewModel
@using DavidBrowning.Admin.Controllers
@using DavidBrowning.Admin.ViewModels
@using DavidBrowning.Admin.ViewModels.Work
@{
	bool isEditMode = Model.EditMode == EditModes.Edit;
	string formAction = isEditMode ? nameof(WorkController.ExperienceEdit) :
		  nameof(WorkController.ExperienceCreate);
	string htmxTarget = isEditMode ?
			 AdminOffcanvasIds.BodySelector(WorkAdminIds.ExperienceEditOffcanvas) :
			 $"#{WorkAdminIds.ExperienceCreateRegion}";
	string overlaySelector = isEditMode ?
			 AdminOffcanvasIds.OverlaySelector(WorkAdminIds.ExperienceEditOffcanvas) :
			 $"#{WorkAdminIds.ExperienceCreateOverlay}";

	string editorId = isEditMode ?
		  $"experience-edit-{Model.Id}" : $"experience-create";
}

<section class="card">
	<div class="card-body">
		<h2>
			@(isEditMode ? "Edit work experience" : "Create work experience")
		</h2>
		@if (isEditMode)
		{
			<p class="card-text text-secondary">
				Edit @Model.CompanyName work experience
			</p>
		}
		else
		{
			<p class="card-text text-secondary">
				New work experience
			</p>
		}
		<div class="admin-form-region">
			<form method="post" asp-controller="Work" asp-action="@formAction"
				  data-experience-edit-form
				  data-asset-edit-mode="@isEditMode.ToString().ToLowerInvariant()"
				  hx-post="@Url.Action(formAction, "Work")" hx-target="@htmxTarget"
				  hx-swap="innerHTML" hx-disabled-elt="find fieldset"
				  hx-indicator="@overlaySelector"
				  enctype="multipart/form-data" hx-encoding="multipart/form-data">
				<fieldset data-experience-create-form>
					<div asp-validation-summary="ModelOnly" class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
					</div>

					@if (isEditMode)
					{
						<input asp-for="Id" type="hidden" />
					}

					<div class="row mb-3">
						<div class="col-12">
							<label asp-for="CompanyName" class="form-label"></label>
							<input asp-for="CompanyName" class="form-control" autocomplete="off" />
							<span asp-validation-for="CompanyName" class="text-danger"></span>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="row mb-3">
						<div class="col-12">
							<label asp-for="LocationDisplayText" class="form-label"></label>
							<input asp-for="LocationDisplayText" class="form-control" autocomplete="off" />
							<span asp-validation-for="LocationDisplayText" class="text-danger"></span>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="form-check mb-3">
						<input asp-for="IsActive" class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" />
						<label asp-for="IsActive" class="form-check-label">
							Show on work page
						</label>
					</div>

					<div class="row mb-3">
						<div class="col-12">
							<div class="d-flex gap-2">
								<button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">
									Submit
								</button>
								@if (isEditMode)
								{
									<button class="btn btn-outline-secondary"
											type="button" data-bs-dismiss="offcanvas">
										Close
									</button>
								}
								else
								{
									<a class="btn btn-outline-secondary"
									   asp-controller="Work" asp-action="ExperienceIndex">
										Reset
									</a>
								}
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</fieldset>
			</form>
			@if (!isEditMode)
			{
				<div id="@WorkAdminIds.ExperienceCreateOverlay"
					 class="admin-form-overlay htmx-indicator"
					 role="status" aria-live="polite" aria-label="Saving work experience">
					<partial name="_Waiting" />
				</div>
			}
		</div>
		@if (isEditMode)
		{
			<partial name="RoleEditList" model="Model.Roles" />
		}
		else
		{
			<div class="alert alert-secondary mt-4 mb-0">
				Save the work experience before adding roles.
			</div>
		}
	</div>
</section>